      "updated": 1774789507850,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Then I don't care how big your dreams are,\nyou will sabotage your success at every\nturn. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Or9QzvG1JYcpdr_pRFCXo",
      "originalText": "Then I don't care how big your dreams are, you will sabotage your success at every turn. ",
