      "text": "And unless your body learns to feel those emotions\nnow, \nyou will unconsciously sabotage your wealth when it\nfinally arrives.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
