      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The version that plays small. \nThe version that doubts. \nThe version that wants to be liked more than it wants\nto be free. \nThat version has a weak signal. \nThat version begs. \nThat version repels opportunity because it cannot\nhandle responsibility. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "U-tQFxZYasY5s8KulXYG8",
      "originalText": "The version that plays small. \nThe version that doubts. \nThe version that wants to be liked more than it wants to be free. \nThat version has a weak signal. \nThat version begs. \nThat version repels opportunity because it cannot handle responsibility. ",
