      "updated": 1774832075780,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "You could grind endlessly, \nrun yourself into exhaustion, \nbuild businesses, \nclimb corporate ladders, \nstudy strategies, \nbut if the signal you're emitting is one of\ninternal poverty, \nyou will sabotage every gain. \nYou will attract betrayal, delays,\nmiscommunication, missed chances. Why?",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "65i7ti656o6rYtshZfl36",
      "originalText": "You could grind endlessly, \nrun yourself into exhaustion, \nbuild businesses, \nclimb corporate ladders, \nstudy strategies, \nbut if the signal you're emitting is one of internal poverty, \nyou will sabotage every gain. \nYou will attract betrayal, delays, miscommunication, missed chances. Why?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
