      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774833229530,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "That's when people begin to treat you differently. \nThey say, you feel different. \nThey say, something about you has changed. \nThey say, I can't explain it, but I trust you. \nAnd they don't even know why. \nBut you know why. \nIt's because you trained your aura to command respect\nlong before you saw results. \nYou became it on the inside before the world could\nvalidate it on the outside.\nAnd that is the ultimate hack. \nThat is the invisible edge. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "fEkPySCYBWuFC3xF9tKpb",
      "originalText": "That's when people begin to treat you differently. \nThey say, you feel different. \nThey say, something about you has changed. \nThey say, I can't explain it, but I trust you. \nAnd they don't even know why. \nBut you know why. \nIt's because you trained your aura to command respect long before you saw results. \nYou became it on the inside before the world could validate it on the outside.\nAnd that is the ultimate hack. \nThat is the invisible edge. ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
