      "updated": 1774833390165,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "But if you begin to rewire your aura for confidence, and you surround\nyourself with those who speak life, who move with boldness, who\noperate in conviction, your signal strengthens tenfold. ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "BMvuZNlqoIHciy1tB62lq",
