      "updated": 1774834225783,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "You can hustle all day.\n You can network and sell and create content, but if the vibration behind all of\nthat is, I don't deserve it, then your results will mirror your fear, not your\neffort.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "2XVuM6IDnGvuY0YP3BCSO",
      "originalText": "You can hustle all day.\n You can network and sell and create content, but if the vibration behind all of that is, I don't deserve it, then your results will mirror your fear, not your effort.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
